The paper also discusses the competitive ratio of various algorithms, which is a common measure of performance in the field of theoretical computer science and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves analyzing graphs and finding optimal solutions, which falls under the category of discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
